"{\"uid\": \"skift.com-2024-05-29-googles-ai-travel-tools-nycs-room-crunch-and-air-frances-olympics-lounge\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Photo Credit: A new lounge facility will be exclusively available to La Premi\\u00e8re guests.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 88, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Air France  Today's podcast looks at Google's AI travel tools, New York City's room crunch, and an Olympics-aimed airport lounge.\", \"from\": 90, \"to\": 219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 90, \"end\": 100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.584864682715635e-30, \"text\": \"Air France\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\"}, {\"begin\": 127, \"end\": 133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9984065731658113, \"rank\": 0.0015959581227251967, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 136, \"end\": 138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999999984084, \"rank\": 1.616154534982629e-12, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}, {\"begin\": 153, \"end\": 166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999997965006, \"rank\": 2.0350639005130404e-10, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Good morning from Skift.\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 239, \"end\": 244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skift\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Skift\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skift\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's Wednesday, May 29.\", \"from\": 246, \"to\": 269, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's what you need to know about the business of travel today.\", \"from\": 270, \"to\": 334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Apple Podcasts|Spotify|Overcast|Google Podcasts|Amazon Podcasts  Google has made further inroads in the travel industry in recent months withseveral AI-powered products it's launched.\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 401, \"end\": 407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9984065731658113, \"rank\": 0.0015959581227251967, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Travel Technology Reporter Justin Dawes delves into four of them.\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 585, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dawes notes that Google has incorporated new AI features into software for physical products, including mobile phones.\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 604, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9984065731658113, \"rank\": 0.0015959581227251967, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 632, \"end\": 634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999999984084, \"rank\": 1.616154534982629e-12, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A new feature on Android devices enables users to translate content on the screen without having to switch apps.\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 723, \"end\": 730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Play\", \"score\": 0.9999999960589321, \"rank\": 3.940898578946984e-09, \"text\": \"Android\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Play\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Play\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Travel technology firm Sabre recently unveiled a new AI-powered retailing platform for airlines called SabreMosaic, which is meant to help airlines create and sell personalized retail experiences.\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Alaska Airlines is planning to launch a trip planner built with tech from Google.\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1028, \"end\": 1043, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alaska_Airlines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alaska Airlines\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alaska_Airlines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alaska_Airlines\"}, {\"begin\": 1102, \"end\": 1108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9984065731658113, \"rank\": 0.0015959581227251967, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"IHG Hotels & Resorts has plans to release a trip planning tool powered by Google's AI within its One Rewards mobile app later this year.\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1184, \"end\": 1190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9984065731658113, \"rank\": 0.0015959581227251967, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 1193, \"end\": 1195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999999984084, \"rank\": 1.616154534982629e-12, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Next,New York City hotel rates have hit record highs in large part due to a supply crunch, writes Senior Hospitality Editor Sean O'Neill.\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999997965006, \"rank\": 2.0350639005130404e-10, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 1372, \"end\": 1384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Se\\u00e1n_O'Neill\", \"score\": 0.559997636474702, \"rank\": 0.38095238095234807, \"text\": \"Sean O'Neill\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Se\\u00e1n_O'Neill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Se\\u00e1n_O'Neill\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The average nightly room rate in New York City during the first quarter was $231, a nearly 7% jump from last year, according to data firm CoStar.\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999997965006, \"rank\": 2.0350639005130404e-10, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 1525, \"end\": 1531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corrective_Optics_Space_Telescope_Axial_Replacement\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CoStar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corrective_Optics_Space_Telescope_Axial_Replacement\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corrective_Optics_Space_Telescope_Axial_Replacement\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"O'Neill notes one major factor behind the soaring room rates is local authorities essentially banning short-term rentals in the city.\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The New York Times reported short-term rentals represented roughly 10% of the city's travel lodging before the crackdown.\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1667, \"end\": 1685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_New_York_Times\", \"score\": 0.9999999996032329, \"rank\": 3.9406100326536375e-10, \"text\": \"The New York Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_New_York_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_New_York_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The city's move to convert thousands of hotel rooms into lodging for migrants has also contributed to the soaring room rates.\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1915, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The practice has removed about 2% of the city's net hotel rooms from the market compared to pre-Covid levels.\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 2025, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Finally,Air France will open an ultra-exclusive airport lounge ahead of the Paris Olympics, reports Airlines Editor Gordon Smith.\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2156, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2035, \"end\": 2045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.584864682715635e-30, \"text\": \"Air France\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\"}, {\"begin\": 2143, \"end\": 2155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gordon_H._Smith\", \"score\": 0.999999995699909, \"rank\": 4.300166722371607e-09, \"text\": \"Gordon Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gordon_H._Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gordon_H._Smith\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Smith writes the concept of airlines offering exclusive services for premium guests is far from new, he notes Air France is pushing those boundaries further with its new ultra-luxe offering, La Premi\\u00e8re lounge.\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2274, \"end\": 2284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.584864682715635e-30, \"text\": \"Air France\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\"}, {\"begin\": 2355, \"end\": 2366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Premi\\u00e8re_(French_TV_network)\", \"score\": 0.6309649524178635, \"rank\": 0.48403361344536644, \"text\": \"La Premi\\u00e8re\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Premi\\u00e8re_(French_TV_network)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Premi\\u00e8re_(French_TV_network)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Passengers in the lounge have access to a spa as well as a menu curated by prominent chef Alain Ducasse.\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2465, \"end\": 2478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alain_Ducasse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.926526625080269e-27, \"text\": \"Alain Ducasse\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alain_Ducasse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alain_Ducasse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, Air France's premium guests can reserve space in three completely private suites that are adjacent to the main La Premi\\u00e8re lounge.\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2494, \"end\": 2504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.584864682715635e-30, \"text\": \"Air France\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each suite includes a double bedroom, outdoor patio and a dedicated butler on the patio.\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Producer/Presenter: Jose Marmolejos  Tags:air france,google,hotel rates,luxury,nyc,paris,skift podcast\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2735, \"end\": 2750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jos\\u00e9_Marmolejos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jose Marmolejos\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jos\\u00e9_Marmolejos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jos\\u00e9_Marmolejos\"}, {\"begin\": 2757, \"end\": 2767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.584864682715635e-30, \"text\": \"air france\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\"}]}]}"